<DocsLayout title="Expense & Mileage" section="Auxiliary Modules">
  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    Track expenses and mileage in Field Promax for effective record-keeping.
    Technicians can upload receipts and track travel details directly from the mobile app.
  </p>
  <p>
    Quick stops for supplies are common — the mobile app makes it easy to upload receipts,
    preventing loss and ensuring timely reimbursement. Mileage tracking helps monitor daily
    travel to reduce unnecessary miles and save on fuel costs.
  </p>

  <h2>How to Access</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Expenses:</strong> From the mobile app, go to <strong>Work Order</strong> → <strong>Other</strong> → <strong>Expenses</strong></li>
    <li><strong>Mileage:</strong> From the mobile app, go to <strong>Work Order</strong> → <strong>Other</strong> → <strong>Mileage</strong></li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Expense Tracking</h2>
  <img src="/images/auxiliary-modules/auxillarymodules_expense_01.png" alt="Expense Tracking" />

  <h3>Recording Expenses</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Open the work order in the mobile app</li>
    <li>Go to <strong>Other</strong> → <strong>Expenses</strong></li>
    <li>Upload receipt photos</li>
    <li>Enter expense details and amounts</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Mileage Tracking</h2>
  <img src="/images/auxiliary-modules/auxillarymodules_mileage_01.jpg" alt="Mileage Tracking" />

  <h3>Recording Mileage</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Open the work order in the mobile app</li>
    <li>Go to <strong>Other</strong> → <strong>Mileage</strong></li>
    <li>Enter vehicle information</li>
    <li>Record odometer readings</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Reporting</h2>
  <p>
    Run weekly or monthly reports to view expenses and mileage by technician.
    Export data for reimbursement processing.
  </p>

  <h2>Notifications & Permissions</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Only <strong>Administrators</strong> can configure expense and mileage tracking settings</li>
    <li>Technicians can record expenses and mileage via the mobile app</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Tips</h2>
  <div class="callout callout-tip">
    <p>
      <strong>Run reports regularly</strong> (weekly or monthly) to review expenses and mileage.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Upload receipts immediately</strong> to prevent loss and ensure accurate records.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Track mileage daily</strong> to identify opportunities for route optimization.
    </p>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
